cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

The paper deals with deep learning techniques for computer vision tasks, specifically seeded segmentation and image matting. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses unsupervised training of deep neural networks, which falls under the sub-categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the use of energy functions is a common technique in optimization and neural networks, which could place the paper under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper deals with image processing, which could also place it under cs.MM (Multimedia).
